    // How to make coffee // 
    Ingredients:
    - 3 teaspoons of coffee powder
    - 200 ml of milk 
    - chocolate powder
    - 180ml (2 x 1/3 cup) water

add coffee powder to the filter
add twice 1/3 cup of water into the moka pot
wait for the moka pot to boil
add 1/3 cup of milk in the coffee cup
warm the milk for 30sec in the microwave
add 1/4 cup milk in the milk frother
once the coffee appears at the top of the moka pot, add 1/4 cup to the cup of milk
mix it with a spoon
add the frothered milk 
add chocolate powder on top 